title: Russian aviation conducted airstrikes at Starytsya, Kozacha Lopan, Okhrimivka, Zakitne, Ozerne, Mykolayivka, Semenivka, Maysk...
content: Russian aviation conducted airstrikes at Starytsya, Kozacha Lopan, Okhrimivka, Zakitne, Ozerne, Mykolayivka, Semenivka, Mayske, Chasiv Yar, Kostyantynivka, Toretsk, Druzhba, Slovyansk, Oleksandro-Kalynove, Sukha Balka, Lysivka, Romanivka, Dachne, Yantarne, Oleksandropil, Sukhi Yaly, Velyka Novosilka, Temyrivka, Zelene Pole, Novoandriyivka, Bilohirya and Olhivka, - General Staff of Armed Forces of Ukraine reports
